Hello team,
Wanted to warn everyone that https://sandbox.console.instabase.com/sandbox may be unusable for a couple of hours (est 4-5 hours) starting at 9PM EST today for longer term performance improvements. This downtime is need as we (the Cloud Console team) are working to address high consumption of and other performance issues with our DB.

Make sure to prepare all your sandboxes for this!
